#

Basic Beer Bread

70 min
$3.5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

BreadEasyQuick

Description

A simple, hearty bread that pairs perfectly with soups and stews.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 3 cups
  • baking powder: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • beer: 12 ounces (1 can or bottle)
  • butter: 1/4 cup, melted
